<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            color: #161d1f;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: #f4fafd;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #006d37;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.08);
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #006d37;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #3d4a3e;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features li {
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background-color: #f4fafd;
            border-left: 4px solid #006d37;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .features li:before {
            content: "✓ ";
            color: #006d37;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #006d37;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #005a2d;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dde4e6;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #3d4a3e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">🍳 RecipeHub</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Welcome to RecipeHub, {{ user.pseudo }}!</div>

            <div class="description">
                Thank you for joining our community of food enthusiasts! We're thrilled to have you on board.
                RecipeHub is your gateway to discovering, sharing, and mastering delicious recipes from around the world.
            </div>

            <div class="description">
                <strong>Here's what you can do now:</strong>
            </div>

            <ul class="features">
                <li>Browse thousands of recipes from talented chefs</li>
                <li>Save your favorite recipes for quick access</li>
                <li>Create and share your own culinary masterpieces</li>
                <li>Discover recipes by categories and tags</li>
                <li>Connect with a vibrant community of food lovers</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="description">
                To get started, please confirm your email address by clicking the link in the confirmation email we just sent you.
                Once verified, you'll have full access to all RecipeHub features!
            </div>

            <a href="{{ app_url }}" class="cta-button">Explore Recipes Now</a>

            <div class="description">
                <strong>Questions?</strong> Our support team is here to help. Simply reply to this email.
            </div>

            <div class="description">
                Happy cooking!<br>
                <strong>The RecipeHub Team</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                You're receiving this email because you just created a RecipeHub account.
                This is a transactional email—please do not reply.
            </p>
            <p>
                © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} RecipeHub. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
